Similarly, if we check out our form
example from the previous lesson,

25
00:01:23,340 --> 00:01:26,440
that red underline on
the invalid phone number field

26
00:01:26,440 --> 00:01:30,610
is now showing up as sort of
a bright bluish green color.

27
